based on the [docs for the endpoint that you are consuming][1], it says that `characters` is an `array`. So, it&#39;s ok to get that attribute as an String, when you try to deserialize from json to an object, but in the logic applied, you are trying to iterate over that. So, I think what you really want to do is change the type of `characters` attribute from `String` to `String[]`. After that you would need to fix the return type of the getter for that attribute


