  [2]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.desktop/javax/swing/Action.html
  [3]: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/76066029/how-to-make-altv-only-process-one-time-when-held-down-then-released#comment134152932_76066029
  [4]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/uiswing/misc/action.html
  [5]: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/13614887/what-is-a-mnemonic-in-java#13614933
  [6]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.desktop/javax/swing/Action.html#buttonActions
  [7]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.desktop/javax/swing/JComponent.html
  [8]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.desktop/javax/swing/AbstractButton.html#setAction(javax.swing.Action)
  [9]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.desktop/javax/swing/JButton.html
  [10]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.desktop/javax/swing/Action.html#putValue(java.lang.String,java.lang.Object)

